text: Ernest O'Brien (26 August 1900 - 2 November 1935) was an Australian cricketer. He played three first-class matches for New South Wales between 1926/27 and 1927/28. ==See also== * List of New South Wales representative cricketers ==References== ==External links== * Category:1900 births Category:1935 deaths Category:Australian cricketers Category:New South Wales cricketers Category:Cricketers from Sydney
title: Ernest O'Brien (cricketer)
